Hi there! I'd be happy to help you with ad placements. Could you please provide more details about what specific information you're looking for regarding ad placements? This will help me assist you better.

NewsBreak automatically optimizes ad placements to achieve your desired results, so you don't need to select specific placements. We use an unlimited native strategy to decide when and where to run your ads for optimized performance. However, you can trust that we are working on the back-end to allocate your budget to the placements that are achieving your goal CPA (Cost-Per-Action). If you want more details on the types of ad formats and placements available, feel free to check out our guide here: [Types of NewsBreak Ad Formats and Placements](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20229876903053-Types-of-NewsBreak-Ad-Formats-and-Placements).
